{"ID":"20260605141117-pjpe2al","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605141117-pjpe2al","title":"2023年新高考Ⅰ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605141138-4tb9djh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-4tb9djh","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答友人论学"}]},{"ID":"20260605141138-4t69wy2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-4t69wy2","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"林希逸"}]},{"ID":"20260605141138-tsybgse","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-tsybgse","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逐字笺来学转难​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"①"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，逢人个个说曾颜​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"②"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141138-xf7dr6b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-xf7dr6b","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那知剥落皮毛处，不在流传口耳间。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141138-wgc1ute","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-wgc1ute","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"禅要自参求印可，仙须亲炼待丹还。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141138-2l2nexy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-2l2nexy","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卖花担上看桃李，此语吾今忆鹤山​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"③"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141138-trfg39r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141138-trfg39r","updated":"20260605141138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【注】①笺：注释。这里指研读经典。②曾颜：孔子的弟子曾参和颜回。③鹤山：南宋学者魏了翁，号鹤山。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141117-r50vtfb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605141117-r50vtfb","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605141207-se38571","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141207-se38571","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．下列对这首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605141207-1994lag","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141207-1994lag","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．诗的首联描述了当时人们不畏艰难、努力学习圣人之道的学术风气。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141207-cm8l28p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141207-cm8l28p","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．诗人认为，“皮毛”之下精要思想的获得，不能简单依靠口耳相传。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141207-g5ndcn3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141207-g5ndcn3","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．颈联中使用“自”“亲”二字，以强调要获得真正学识必须亲自钻研。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141207-a2roran","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141207-a2roran","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．诗人采用类比等方法阐明他的治学主张，使其浅近明白、通俗易懂。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141207-4hxpyra","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141207-4hxpyra","updated":"20260605141207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．诗的尾联提到魏了翁的名言：“不欲于卖花担上看桃李，须树头枝底方见活精神也。”结合本诗主题，谈谈你对这句话的理解。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141117-q6oeq1e","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605141117-q6oeq1e","updated":"20260605141221"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605141221-9vtv4nl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141221-9vtv4nl","updated":"20260605141221"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．A    16．①卖花担上的桃李，虽然也缤纷绚烂，但活力已经不再。②唯有回归本原，方能获得学问真谛，就如同在树头枝底欣赏桃李，方能体会到其活泼的精神。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141117-iyx14mv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605141117-iyx14mv","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605141234-629zfdq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141234-629zfdq","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生理解诗歌内容，赏析诗歌语言、手法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141234-71yxir7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141234-71yxir7","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“不畏艰难、努力学习圣人之道的学术风气”错误，“学转难”表明用“逐字笺”的学习方法难以理解经典真谛，且“逢人个个说曾颜”也并非指努力学习圣人之道，而是讽刺当下人们对圣人之道的学习流于表面。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141234-qvf8ra1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141234-qvf8ra1","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141234-bpfwyea","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141234-bpfwyea","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．本题考查学生理解诗句内涵，把握诗歌主题的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141234-9krtdt7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141234-9krtdt7","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由题干可知，首先要把握魏了翁名言的意思。“不欲于卖花担上看桃李，须树头枝底方见活精神也”是说在树头枝底观赏桃李才能体会到其活泼泼的精神状态。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141234-cxtg74m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141234-cxtg74m","updated":"20260605141234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接着把握本诗尾联的内容并结合诗歌的主题来谈自己的理解。“卖花担上看桃李，此语吾今忆鹤山”是说大家在肩挑的担子上观看鲜花，在喧闹的酒楼上欣赏音乐，根本想象不到桃李绽放的盛况，也不可能体会到丝竹管弦的精妙。结合诗歌的标题“答友人论学”可知，此处用“看桃李”来喻指做学问，以“树头枝底”来喻指学问的本源，诗人以此说明要想获得学问的真谛需要回归本源，这就如同观赏桃李，卖花担上的桃李虽美，但离开“树头枝底”，没有了活力，唯有到树头枝底才能体会到其活泼的精神状态。"}]}]}